listings.description:
Porsche Centre Leeds are proud to offer this 2020 Taycan Turbo S. Finished in Jet Black Metallic and complemented by Two-Tone Leather Interior, Smooth-Finish Leather, Black/Chalk Beige. This vehicle features an extensive specification including Carbon SportDesign Package, 21-inch Taycan Exclusive Design Wheels, 4+1 Seats, Sport Chrono Stopwatch Instrument Dial White, Heated Race-Tex steering wheel (for leather interior with Sport Chrono), Passenger Display, Burmester® 3D High-End Surround Sound System, Exclusive Matrix LED headlights in Glacier Ice Blue with Porsche Dynamic Light System Plus, Panoramic fixed glass roof, Acoustically insulated laminated privacy glass, Lane Change Assist, ParkAssist including Surround View and Porsche InnoDrive with Active Lane Keeping and Adaptive Cruise Control. This vehicle has a complete Porsche service history and benefits from being a 2 owner vehicle.
A comprehensive Porsche 111-point mechanical check and thorough cosmetic preparation has been completed on this vehicle, which will also be supplied with the peerless 2-year Porsche Approved Warranty.
It would be our pleasure to have you visit our centre to view the car and discuss how we can make your dream Porsche a reality. We also offer specialist funding packages which we would be happy to guide you through. To Arrange a viewing, test drive or a detailed video please contact a member of the sales team who will be more than happy to help.
